{"tid":267251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[相］App相識賓館談心　青年涉亮刀搶27歲女網友電話","createTime":"2017-06-02T06:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T17:20:22.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"006075e9d5c922bb6afb43e3682da286aff1ca61","tid":267251,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T06:49:45.000Z","msg":"21歲無業青年，在去年7月透過手機程式認識一名年齡比自己大7年的女子後，兩人相約外出見面，青年又邀請女子到其暫住的賓館談心。惟青年帶女子到賓館後，涉嫌亮利刀，要求女子交出手提電話，女子最後奪門而逃及報警。青年鍾天賜事被捕，今在區域法院否認一項企圖搶劫罪受審。<br />\n<br />\n27歲蔡姓女事主作供稱............<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170602/bkn-20170602133221122-0602_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170602%2Fbkn-20170602133221122-0602_00822_001.html&d=i9aJShi6wDRnb7T0HJaU7v7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=6a6a0264\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170602/bkn-20170602133221122-0602_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/02/144941_d9487d946c4330cf98b58981cb091846.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F02%2F144941_d9487d946c4330cf98b58981cb091846.jpg&h=ed5735ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f7d7243e30649b7206632199edadac8a79ff24c","tid":267251,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T06:54:10.000Z","msg":"樓豬？"},{"pid":"660de9d232ac351bdeda5fecd676107441e6525a","tid":267251,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T06:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/02/145442_a8fb42a2aca4548dc812374ddab87441.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F02%2F145442_a8fb42a2aca4548dc812374ddab87441.jpg&h=ac503623&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5bf11e3ce86c6c583e53f7d08bcf45ea219dd74f","tid":267251,"uid":1705,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score